{"timestamp":1774434887910,"source_app":"agentic-harness","session_id":"5b3a1817-1c0c-4474-899b-a93378841e0c","hook_event_type":"PostToolUse","tool_name":"Read","tool_use_id":"toolu_01HXus28Ti46g9T2QNgEaRZL","payload":{"session_id":"5b3a1817-1c0c-4474-899b-a93378841e0c","transcript_path":"/Users/auto/.claude/projects/-Users-auto-agentic-harness-apps-mas-trees-ac449148/5b3a1817-1c0c-4474-899b-a93378841e0c.jsonl","cwd":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/ac449148","permission_mode":"bypassPermissions","hook_event_name":"PostToolUse","tool_name":"Read","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/ac449148/specs/issue-ac449148-adw-3f228a76-sdlc_planner-remove-ctas-photoshop-plans.md"},"tool_response":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/ac449148/specs/issue-ac449148-adw-3f228a76-sdlc_planner-remove-ctas-photoshop-plans.md","content":"# Plan: Remove CTAs from Photoshop Plans page\n\n## Task Description\nRemove all Call-to-Action (CTA) elements from the Photoshop Plans page. CTAs are defined as:\n- `<a is=\"checkout-link\">` elements with action labels (e.g. \"Buy now\")\n- Their containing `<div slot=\"footer\">` wrapper if it serves no other purpose after removal\n\nThe target page is the plans test/demo HTML file that renders Photoshop plan card templates. The `footer` slot and its checkout-link buttons must be removed from all photoshop-related templates. Informational content (pricing, descriptions, icons) must be preserved.\n\n## Relevant Files\n\n- `web-components/test/merch-card.plans.test.html` \u2014 Main target: contains `photoshop` and `photoshop-with-addon` templates, each with a `<div slot=\"footer\">` holding a \"Buy now\" `<a is=\"checkout-link\">` CTA. These are the CTAs to remove.\n- `web-components/src/variants/plans.js` \u2014 Read to understand `PLANS_AEM_FRAGMENT_MAPPING.ctas` slot mapping (footer slot). No changes needed here unless the mapping itself drives CTA rendering for the target page.\n- `web-components/test/mocks/sites/fragments/fragment-photoshop.json` \u2014 Mock AEM fragment with `ctas` field containing a \"Buy now\" checkout-link. May need the `ctas` field emptied if it drives CTA rendering on the plans page.\n- `web-components/test/mocks/sites/fragments/fragment-photography-plans.json` \u2014 Check for CTA field, remove if present.\n\n## Step by Step Tasks\n\n### 1. Remove CTA from `photoshop` template\n- In `web-components/test/merch-card.plans.test.html`, locate the `<template id=\"photoshop\">` block (lines 25\u201374)\n- Remove the entire `<div slot=\"footer\">...</div>` block containing the \"Buy now\" `<a is=\"checkout-link\">` element (lines 62\u201372)\n\n### 2. Remove CTA from `photoshop-with-addon` template\n- In the same file, locate `<template id=\"photoshop-with-addon\">` (lines 82\u2013153)\n- Remove the entire `<div slot=\"footer\">...</div>` block containing the \"Buy now\" `<a is=\"checkout-link\">` element (lines 141\u2013151)\n\n### 3. Audit fragment-photoshop.json for CTA field\n- Read `web-components/test/mocks/sites/fragments/fragment-photoshop.json`\n- If the `ctas` field contains a checkout-link/button, clear its value to an empty HTML string or remove the field if the schema permits\n- This prevents fragment-driven CTA rendering on the photoshop plans page\n\n### 4. Audit fragment-photography-plans.json for CTA field\n- Read `web-components/test/mocks/sites/fragments/fragment-photography-plans.json`\n- Apply the same treatment as step 3 if a CTA is present\n\n### 5. Verify no orphaned markup or empty containers remain\n- After removals, confirm no empty `<div slot=\"footer\"></div>` wrappers remain in the photoshop templates\n- Confirm no unused `data-analytics-id`, `data-wcs-osi`, or `data-template` attributes are left as orphans\n- Confirm the file parses as valid HTML (`node --check` is not applicable to HTML, but validate manually or with a linter)\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- The `photoshop` template in `merch-card.plans.test.html` has no `<div slot=\"footer\">` or `<a is=\"checkout-link\">` elements\n- The `photoshop-with-addon` template in `merch-card.plans.test.html` has no `<div slot=\"footer\">` or `<a is=\"checkout-link\">` elements\n- All informational content (icons, heading, pricing, description, addon) is unchanged\n- The `ctas` field in `fragment-photoshop.json` is empty or removed (no \"Buy now\" link)\n- Existing unit tests in `merch-card.plans.test.html` script block still pass (the tests only check rendering/existence of the card, not CTA presence)\n- No empty wrapper divs or orphaned attributes remain where CTAs were\n\n## Validation Commands\n- `node --check web-components/src/variants/plans.js` \u2014 verify no JS syntax errors if plans.js is touched\n- `node --check web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js` \u2014 verify CSS module syntax if touched\n","numLines":52,"startLine":1,"totalLines":52}},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HXus28Ti46g9T2QNgEaRZL"}}
